****[INSTALLING THE MINECRAFTIA FONT]***
****************************************

TO ENHANCE THE VISUAL APPEAL, THIS PROGRAM UTILIZES THE MINECRAFTIA FONT FOR DISPLAY TEXT.
EASILY INSTALL THIS FONT BY FOLLOWING THESE STEPS:

	1.) LOCATE THE 'Minecraftia-Regular.ttf' FONT FILE IN THE INSTALL FOLDER.
	2.) OPEN THE FILE AND SELECT "INSTALL."
	3.) ONCE INSTALLED, LAUNCH THE MINECRAFT SERVER LAUNCHER TO SEE THE CHANGE.
	4.) NOW, YOU CAN APPLY THE MINECRAFTIA FONT TO ANY APPLICATION SUPPORTING TRUE TYPE FONTS.

